overview:
Yamie Chess Ltd is a K-8 educational learning company for STEM education (Science, Technology, Engineering and Mathematics) focused on supporting children’s learning in the K-8 Elementary and Middle School stages of education, to help children reach their full intellectual potential in school mathematics, logic and science education, for college careers ahead.

Made In America, the first Yamie Chess™ School Assistant (The Adventures of Tigermore & The Mind Angels™) for K-8 math learning is being launched simultaneously at NSSEA Ed Expo 2014 and American International Toy Fair 2014 in New York City.

Yamie Chess Ltd has a professional animation studio division as part of the company, to bring the Yamie Chess™ educational cartoon character properties to life, to inspire children’s imagination. The company’s first animated short film, King Tigermore In Strawberry Fields, will be launched at San Diego Comic Con 2014 and the American International Toy Fair 2014.

Yamie Chess Ltd is 100% committed to American manufacturing. All Yamie Chess™ products use 100% U.S. labor, 100% U.S. craftsmanship and American materials that are 98% sourced from heartland America. Yamie Chess Ltd works in manufacturing partnership with EPI Printers, Inc, based in Battle Creek, MI, a 50-year old, ISO 9001:2008 certified American manufacturer established in 1959.
